cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new embedding learning method. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving the performance of NLP tasks using machine learning techniques. It could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the semantic understanding of words, which is important in information retrieval tasks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks to learn the embeddings.
